      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Peter Österlund</b>\n</p><p><b>Peter Österlund</b>,<br />\na Swedish computer scientist and chess programmer. He is author of <a href=\"/MLChess\" title=\"MLChess\">MLChess</a>, a machine language chess program for the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HP_48_series\">HP 48 series</a> of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graphing_calculator\">Graphing calculators</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, developed since 1995  <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a> open source chess engine <a href=\"/CuckooChess\" title=\"CuckooChess\">CuckooChess</a>, both under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL</a>. Peter Österlund further ported <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> to the <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a> platform, called <a href=\"/DroidFish\" title=\"DroidFish\">DroidFish</a>, with <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> and <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening book</a> code, derived from CuckooChess <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Texel\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Texel</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Texel\">Texel</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Texel\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In March 2012, Peter Österlund announced and published his new engine <a href=\"/Texel\" title=\"Texel\">Texel</a>. Texel 1.00 was functionally equivalent to an unreleased version of CuckooChess. The main difference is that Texel is written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++11</a> instead of <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/comp.sys.hp48/FWmYmytpmwg/R5mt8DCZlHcJ\">MLChess V1.01</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/comp.sys.hp48\">comp.sys.hp48</a>, December 17, 1995</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/comp.sys.hp48/hPZF-1AFo4E/0fb14iuzbjYJ\">MLChess 1.09</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/comp.sys.hp48\">comp.sys.hp48</a>, May 08, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/comp.sys.hp48/ZtVPbkjGZWs/IV06qlXTlvoJ\">MLChess V1.11 with experimental HP49 support</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/comp.sys.hp48\">comp.sys.hp48</a>, March 12, 2000</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=360726\">Re: Revolutionizing handheld chess: Glaurung 2 for the iPhone</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 08, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=419103\">Summary of Monte Carlo results for perft(12) so far</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 13, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=430593\">CuckooChess 1.12</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 24, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42999\">New chess engine: Texel</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 24, 2012 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43134\">Elo versus speed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 02, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Depth#DiminishingReturns\" title=\"Depth\">Diminishing Returns</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48752\">Recursive DTS-like search algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>, <a href=\"/Recursion\" title=\"Recursion\">Recursion</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48780\">Time to depth measuring tool</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Depth\" title=\"Depth\">Depth</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=555522&amp;t=50823\">The texel evaluation function optimization algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 31, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a>, <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60833\">How texel probes endgame tablebases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 16, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Gaviota_Tablebases\" title=\"Gaviota Tablebases\">Gaviota Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a>, <a href=\"/Texel\" title=\"Texel\">Texel</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64824\">Lazy SMP and \"lazy cluster\" experiments</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 06, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP#LazyCluster\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP - Lazy Cluster</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64824&amp;start=43\">Approximate ABDADA</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Österlund</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/ABDADA\" title=\"ABDADA\">ABDADA</a> </dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hem.bredband.net/petero2b/index.html\">Welcome to Peter Österlund's home page!</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hem.bredband.net/petero2b/javachess/index.html\">CuckooChess - A Java Chess Program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://market.android.com/developer?pub=Peter+%C3%96sterlund\">Apps von Peter Österlund - Android Market</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_%C3%96sterlund&amp;action